If you know they are a genuine member of the projects you can manage, please assign him/her to the projects by:
- Go to http://localhost/people/2
- Choose 'Person Administration'
- At the bottom. you will see the list of projects and institutions that you can assign this person to

If the institution does not exist, you can create the new institution. To do this:
- Go to Institutions tab
- Choose 'New Institution'
After the institution has been created successfully, you need to assign it to the project that you manage, by:
- Select the project
- Choose 'Project administration'
- You will see the list institutions that you can select to assign to this project

